text: Nagma Shrestha (Nepali: नगमा श्रेष्ठ) (born 10 November 1991) in Kathmandu, Nepal is a Nepali Model, Television presenter & producer. She is also the title winner of Miss Earth Nepal 2012Nagma Shrestha is Miss Nepal Earth 2012 & directly nominated for Miss Universe Nepal 2017 by the organizer and represented Nepal in Miss Universe 2017. She completed her +2 study from United Academy & bachelors in business study from Time Business School. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners Category:Living people Category:People from Kathmandu Category:Nepalese models
